OL,3,CWorld champion kickboxer charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of teen
OL,6,FA world champion kickboxer will face
OL,7,Ftrial next year, accused of murdering
OL,8,Fa teenager who died in a fatal road
OL,9,Fcollision.
OL,11,FTyler Ford, 18, appeared before
OL,12,FSwansea Crown Court on Tuesday 14 July
OL,13,Faccused of killing Ceiran Evans from
OL,14,FGorseinon, Swansea.
OL,16,FIt comes after police were called to
OL,17,FPen Cae Crwn Road, in Swansea, at 1pm
OL,18,Fon Thursday 9 July, following a report
OL,19,Fof a collision involving a car and an
OL,20,Foff-road bike.
