OL,3,CWorld champion kickboxer charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of teen
OL,6,FThe 18-year-old, who has been a world
OL,7,Fkickboxing champion nine times, has
OL,8,Falso been charged with the attempted
OL,9,Fmurder of a second person.
OL,11,FDuring a hearing at Swansea Crown
OL,12,FCourt, the defendant spoke only to
OL,13,Fconfirm his name during the brief
OL,14,Fadministrative hearing, and was asked
OL,15,Fnot to enter any pleas.
OL,17,FJudge Paul Thomas KC fixed a plea and
OL,18,Fcase management hearing for September
OL,19,F29 and said a two-week trial will
OL,20,Fbegin on January 11 2027.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
