OL,3,CWorld champion kickboxer charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of teen
OL,6,FRemanding Tyler Ford into custody, the
OL,7,Fjudge said: "The next hearing will be
OL,8,FSeptember 29 and the defendant will of
OL,9,Fcourse remain in custody."
OL,11,FThe family of Ceiran Evans paid
OL,12,Ftribute to him on Monday.
OL,14,FThey described him as having a "kind
OL,15,Fheart" and "loving nature" and said he
OL,16,Fwill always be remembered.
